reviews.review_text: Great Matrix great show. While you may not find a premier version of any given song in here, this one has all the components of a top-notch show.  First Set gives an excellent run of "new" tunes with Victim, Built To Last, and Blow Away.  Second Set efficiently makes its way through some heavy selections, including of course the Death Don't.  9 minutes Franklin's is plenty; I don't care so much for the versions that go on and on.  Gotta give this one 5.0 Swami stars overall.
